A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Illegal Dumping and Litter Control Law – Video Evidence and Reward
3 Programs
4 FOR the purpose of requiring each county to establish a certain program allowing a member
5 of the public to submit video evidence of an alleged violation of the Illegal Dumping
6 and Litter Control Law to a certain enforcement unit; requiring a program
7 established under this Act to allow a member of the public to receive a portion of
8 fines collected in relation to a violation of the Illegal Dumping and Litter Control
9 Law under certain circumstances; and generally relating to illegal dumping and
10 litter control video evidence and reward programs.
